1. Creating a Shared Directory

Command used:
sudo mkdir /var/soc_shared  - text in red


2. Assigning Ownership
Command:
sudo chown zakariya:socmonitor /var/soc_shared


3. Setting Permissions (chmod)
Command:
sudo chmod 750 /var/soc_shared


4. Switching to SOC Analyst User
Command:
sudo -i -u socmonitor

5. Testing Access as socmonitor
Commands:
cd /var/soc_shared
pwd
whoami

6. Attempting File Creation (Expected Failure)
Command:
touch test.txt

7. Verifying from Admin User
Command:
exit
ls /var/soc_shared
